title: Paysafe card not workin to me help pls
body: It is telling me like wrong pin number and tranzation faild

replies.body: Not sure why that error is happening for you, but we can take a look!  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and our billing team will help individually with this.  We'll get back to you!
